Hello,

I was wondering if someone is selling their Rev Robotics Mini Power Module (SKU: REV-11-1956) ??

We made the mistake of designing our product to fit exactly the shape of this fuse box, unfortunately, REV Robotics has no stock and the lead time is approximately 6 months for production.
